node.text:
this piece is a fanart for @fresh_bobatae and also a tablet review! 
✨artist pro 16TP review ✨
@xppen_usa recently sent me the Artist Pro 16TP to review! This tablet is fantastic and I love the touch screen display. The touch screen is really helpful and practical, and the tablet itself is gorgeous and works great for drawing. I also like the pen as the pen sensitivity works wonderfully and I like the colors on the display as well. This tablet is really dreamy because the visual display is so amazing, vivid, and colorful, and it's quite fun to draw on. The detail and clarity of the screen really help me paint out my ideas and express myself, and the colors are so accurate and natural that it makes choosing color palettes a breeze. The touch-screen function helps me zoom in and out, which makes the drawing process more convenient and makes accessing the controls easier. The tablet is also easy to set up with 2 USB-C ports and the connection is smooth and works well. There's even an eraser at one end of the pen, which helps even more with lineart and coloring! The Artist Pro 16TP is really comfortable to use and I feel like I can fully utilize my creativity while drawing on it. I love how immersive, responsive, and perfect this tablet is. Overall, I highly recommend this tablet! If you'd like to purchase it, here are the purchase links:

Official US store: https://bit.ly/3eVo9oy
Official Canada store: https://bit.ly/3kWl8YY

The tablet is provided 20% off during XP Pen's 16th anniversary. 
There's also an additional 5% off coupon for anyone who would like to purchase it. The coupon code is "acatcie16tp" and is valid until the end of the anniversary. It is only available in XP-Pen's official US and Canada store.
.
the characters in the piece are from @fresh_bobatae bts love yourself album drawings!! i really love their designs so i had to draw them🌸💞

🎨huion kamvas 16 (2021) review🎨
a big thanks to @huiontablet @huioncanada for sending me this tablet and giving me the opportunity to review it! if you’d like to know more about the product, check out the link in my highlights!🌸
overall i really really like this tablet; it runs smoothly and responsively and the shortcut buttons help a lot with my drawing process! the pen pressure is great and this tablet is really comfortable and fun to use! for anyone looking into digital art or in need of a tablet, i definitely recommend the huion kamvas 16 (2021)🌱
thank you so much @huioncanada @huiontablet for being patient with me for this collaboration!💞
.
